#: ../../source/administration.rst:2959
msgid "|image233|"
msgstr "|image233|"

#: ../../source/administration.rst:2961
msgid "'Z39.50 server' should be populated with a name that will help you identify the source (such as the library name)."
msgstr "'Z39.50 伺服器' 應給個便於辨認的名稱 (如圖書館名)。"

#: ../../source/administration.rst:2964 ../../source/administration.rst:3091
msgid "'Hostname' will be the address to the Z39.50 target."
msgstr "'主機名稱' 是指 Z39.50 目標的網址。"

#: ../../source/administration.rst:2966 ../../source/administration.rst:3093
msgid "'Port' tells Koha what port to listen on to get results from this target."
msgstr "'連接埠' 是指Koha取得資料的目標連接埠。"

#: ../../source/administration.rst:2969 ../../source/administration.rst:3096
msgid "'Userid' and 'Password' are only required for servers that are password protected."
msgstr "'使用者帳號' 與 '密碼' 是伺服器要求的。"

#: ../../source/administration.rst:2972 ../../source/administration.rst:3099
